  "texts": [
    "This feature allows them to grow their knowledge and skills adapted to their demand when operating and maintaining the factory.",
    "Benefits of implementing the GPT industrial bot over conventional smart dashboards and human-machine interfaces (HMIs)Several tools and devices are being implemented in the industrial sector to facilitate the interaction between operators and factory equipment regarding monitoring and controlling processes.",
    "These tools are smart dashboards, digital panels, and human-machine interfaces (HMIs) [54].",
    "While these devices successfully perform their intended monitoring and control tasks in various industrial and manufacturing applications, they have shortcomings when considering I5.0 exigences.",
    "Under I5.0, HMIs are evolving [51] from simple monitoring and control graphical tools to more interactive systems with more supporting functionalities for operators."
